Uses of Package
board

  • Packages that use board 
    Package Description
    autoroute
    Contains functionality of the autoroute algorithm.
    board
    Contains classes describing items on a printed circuit board and the board itself.
    boardgraphics
    Contains user interface independent functionality for displaying a board on a sccreen.
    designformats.specctra
    Contains classes for reading and writing board designs in the Specctra dsn text format.
    gui
    Contains functionality of the graphical user interface based on javax.swing.
    interactive
    Contains functionality for interactive board handling, which is independent of the graphical user interface.
    library
    Describes library objects of a printed circuit board such as padstacks and component packages.
    rules
    Contains rules and restrictions for the items on a printed circuit board.
    tests
    Contains functions for testing and checking the consistancy of the board database.
  • Classes in board used by autoroute 
    Class and Description
    AngleRestriction
    Enum for angle restrictions none, fortyfive degree and ninety degree.
    Item
    Basic class of the items on a board.
    RoutingBoard
    Contains higher level functions of a board
    SearchTreeObject
    Common ShapeSearchTree functionality for board.Items and autoroute.ExpansionRooms
    ShapeSearchTree
    Elementary geometric search functions making direct use of the MinAreaTree in the package datastructures.
    TestLevel
    If > RELEASE, some features may be used, which are still in experimental state.
  • Classes in board used by board 
    Class and Description
    AngleRestriction
    Enum for angle restrictions none, fortyfive degree and ninety degree.
    BasicBoard
    Provides basic functionality of a board with geometric items.
    BoardObservers
    BoardObservers interface.
    BoardOutline
    Class describing a board outline.
    CalcFromSide
    CalcFromSide class.
    ClearanceViolation
    Information of a clearance violation between 2 items.
    Communication
    Communication information to host systems or host design formats.
    Communication.SpecctraParserInfo
    Information from the parser scope in a Specctra-dsn-file.
    Communication.SpecctraParserInfo.WriteResolution 
    Component
    Describes board components consisting of an array of pins und other stuff like component keepouts.
    ComponentObstacleArea
    Describes areas of the board, where components arre not allowed.
    ComponentOutline
    ComponentOutline class.
    Components
    Contains the lists of components on the board.
    ConductionArea
    A ObstacleArea, which can be electrically conected to other items.
    Connectable
    Functionality required for items, which can be electrical connected to other items.
    DrillItem
    Common superclass for Pins and Vias
    FixedState
    Sorted fixed states of board items.
    ForcedPadAlgo.CheckDrillResult 
    Item
    Basic class of the items on a board.
    Item.StopConnectionOption
    Used as parameter of get_connection to control, that the connection stops at the next fanout via or at any via.
    ItemSelectionFilter
    Filter for selecting items on the board.
    ItemSelectionFilter.SelectableChoices
    The possible choices in the filter.
    Layer
    Describes the structure of a board layer.
    LayerStructure
    Describes the layer structure of the board.
    ObjectInfoPanel
    Output window for printing information about board objects.
    ObjectInfoPanel.Printable
    Funktionality needed for objects to print information into an ObjectInfoWindow
    ObstacleArea
    An item on the board with an relative_area shape, for example keepout, conduction relative_area
    Pin
    Class describing the functionality of an electrical Item on the board with a shape on 1 or several layers.
    Pin.TraceExitRestriction
    Describes an exit restriction from a trace from a pin pad.
    PolylineTrace
    Objects of class Trace, whose geometry is described by a Polyline
    PrintableShape
    Shape class used for printing a geometry.planar.Shape after transforming it to user coordinates.
    PullTightAlgo
    Class with functionality for optimising traces and vias.
    RoutingBoard
    Contains higher level functions of a board
    SearchTreeManager
    SearchTreeManager class.
    SearchTreeObject
    Common ShapeSearchTree functionality for board.Items and autoroute.ExpansionRooms
    ShapeSearchTree
    Elementary geometric search functions making direct use of the MinAreaTree in the package datastructures.
    TestLevel
    If > RELEASE, some features may be used, which are still in experimental state.
    Trace
    Class describing functionality required for traces in the plane.
    Unit
    Enum for the userunits inch, mil or millimeter.
    Via
    Class describing the functionality of an electrical Item on the board, which may have a shape on several layer, whose geometry is described by a padstack.
    ViaObstacleArea
    Describes Areas on the board, where vias are not allowed.
